  "title": "Heidelberg Q4",
  "body": "What does the law of God require of us?\n\nChrist teaches us in sum, Matt 22:37-40: Thou shalt love the Lord thy God with all thy heart, with all thy soul, with all thy mind, and with all thy strength. This is the first and the great commandment. And the second is like unto it: Thou shalt love thy neighbor as thyself. On these two commandments hang all the law and the prophets.",
